text: Rakul Vesturdal Magnussen (born 3 April 1988) is a Faroese footballer who plays as a midfielder for 1. deild kvinnur club EB/Streymur/Skála. She has been a member of the Faroe Islands women's national team. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Faroese women's footballers Category:Faroe Islands women's international footballers
